♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

462
00:26:33,670 --> 00:26:36,990
♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

463
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:40,650
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

464
00:26:41,150 --> 00:26:44,120
♪Returning to the land
Left bare by the receding sea♪

465
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:47,010
♪Withering like a fallen leaf♪

466
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:50,520
♪The message in a bottle
buried on the shore♪

467
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:53,520
♪No one asked♪

468
00:26:54,470 --> 00:27:00,080
♪All this lonely courage for myself♪

469
00:27:00,750 --> 00:27:06,800
♪I'm no longer part of your world♪

470
00:27:06,970 --> 00:27:10,570
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

471
00:27:10,650 --> 00:27:13,660
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

472
00:27:13,710 --> 00:27:17,130
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

473
00:27:17,370 --> 00:27:20,240
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

474
00:27:20,340 --> 00:27:23,970
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

475
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:27,180
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

476
00:27:27,330 --> 00:27:33,290
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

477
00:27:33,650 --> 00:27:37,390
♪If the sea didn't wait
for the evening breeze♪

478
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:40,260
♪And swim with me to you♪

479
00:27:40,310 --> 00:27:43,850
♪I'd become♪

480
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:46,910
♪A whale
who forever keeps the sea company♪

481
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:50,580
♪If love is like a night storm♪

482
